## Project Outcome

This project showed that machine learning can be trained to predict asthma based on symptoms and related features. The work also demonstrated that visualization and clustering are valuable for understanding the dataset beyond pure prediction.

The project combined both predictive modelling and exploratory analysis, making it a strong example of practical healthcare-focused machine learning using structured tabular data.

